ack\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104exm1665702661663.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/exm1665702661663.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/exm1665702661663.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"exm1665702661663\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      step size\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"exm1665702661663__step_size_146357\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the number of rows the connector selects from the DBMS in each step of the Uniface stepped hitlist.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"exm1665702661663__topic_d48068e1_d48069e1_d48070e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exm1665702661663__d6142e17\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var>_PARAMS = step size :</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">single</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exm1665702661663__d6142e32\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$<var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var>_PARAMS = step :</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">single</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exm1665702661663__topic_d31487e1_d31488e1_d31489e1_d31490e1_d31491e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d203118e86\">\n                        \n Use\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__1\">\n Applies to\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__2\">\n Mnemonic\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__3\">\n Connector Syntax\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__1\">\n DB2 connector\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__2\">\n DB2\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__1\">\n MS SQL connector\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__2\">\n MSS\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__1\">\n MySQL connector\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__2\">\n MQL\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$MQL_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__1\">\n ODBC connector\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__2\">\n ODx\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exm1665702661663__table_d4547e1_d4548e1_d4549e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ODx_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exm1665702661663__topic_d31492e1_d31493e1_d31494e1_d31495e1_d31496e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d203118e194\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exm1665702661663__p_d48083e1_d48084e1_d48085e1\">This option specifies the step size of the Uniface stepped hitlist mechanism. The number specified must be in the range from 0 through 32,767. If you specify 0, the stepped hitlist mechanism is disabled, causing Uniface to internally finish the hitlist each time, before returning control to the application.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exm1665702661663__p_d48086e1_d48087e1_d48088e1\">If not specified, the step size defaults to 10.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"exm1665702661663__note_w2902ab1b5b7b7_w2903ab1b5b7_w2904ab1b5_w2905ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If printing large amounts of data\n      in batch mode with the <code class=\"ph codeph\">Clear (C)</code> printing option, it is not advisable to\n      disable the stepped hitlist. Without the stepped hitlist, Uniface would have to select\n      everything before starting to format the print file; the time gained with the\n        <code class=\"ph codeph\">C</code> option would be lost.</div>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS step size : 100</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gwm1665702661923.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Stepped Hitlists</a><p>Uniface uses the Select request to create a partially built hitlist called a stepped hitlist. This mechanism ensures that a limited number of occurrences are fetched from the database, even though a large number of occurrences match the retrieve profile entered by the user.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527381\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527381\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "step size Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 step size Set the number of rows the connector selects from the DBMS in each step of the Uniface stepped hitlist. USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = step size : Number | single USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = step : Number | single Use Applies to Mnemonic Connector Syntax DB2 connector DB2 USYS$DB2_PARAMS MS SQL connector MSS USYS$MSS_PARAMS MySQL connector MQL USYS$MQL_PARAMS ODBC connector ODx USYS$ODx_PARAMS Description This option specifies the step size of the Uniface stepped hitlist mechanism. The number specified must be in the range from 0 through 32,767. If you specify 0, the stepped hitlist mechanism is disabled, causing Uniface to internally finish the hitlist each time, before returning control to the application. If not specified, the step size defaults to 10. Note: If printing large amounts of data in batch mode with the Clear (C) printing option, it is not advisable to disable the stepped hitlist. Without the stepped hitlist, Uniface would have to select everything before starting to format the print file; the time gained with the C option would be lost. USYS$MSS_PARAMS step size : 100 Copy Related Links Stepped Hitlists Uniface uses the Select request to create a partially built hitlist called a stepped hitlist. This mechanism ensures that a limited number of occurrences are fetched from the database, even though a large number of occurrences match the retrieve profile entered by the user. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}